      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "40914-40946",
      "markText": "日子一天一天地过去，卡拉不再朝那一带走了。她抵抗着那样做的诱惑。",
      "totalCount": 1410,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=40914&rangeEnd=40946",
