    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_4_388-409",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "388-409",
      "markText": "是什么让你那么确定：自己不是邪恶的那一个？",
      "totalCount": 1300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=388&rangeEnd=409",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=388&rangeEnd=409"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_6_7895-7967",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "7895-7967",
      "markText": "生活中最令人沮丧的事情之一就是，有时候会遇到一些笨嘴拙舌、孤独而又没有吸引力的男子，他们赤裸裸地向她示意，让她明白，她跟他们一样同是天涯沦落人。",
      "totalCount": 1152,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7895&rangeEnd=7967",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=7895&rangeEnd=7967"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_5_40141-40204",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "40141-40204",
      "markText": "她像是肺里什么地方扎进去了一根致命的针，浅一些呼吸时可能不感到疼。可是每当她需要深深吸进去一口气时，她便能觉出那根针依然存在。",
      "totalCount": 1110,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=40141&rangeEnd=40204",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=40141&rangeEnd=40204"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_6_35870-35926",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "35870-35926",
      "markText": "虽然她永远也没有完全抛弃那种隐隐嘲笑朱丽叶的习惯，那无非是一个潜藏的竞争对手心中惯常会兴起的醋波微澜的一种反映。",
      "totalCount": 1098,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=35870&rangeEnd=35926",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=35870&rangeEnd=35926"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_5_3509-3526",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3509-3526",
      "markText": "“脾气不火暴还算得上是男子汉吗？”",
      "totalCount": 1050,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3509&rangeEnd=3526",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3509&rangeEnd=3526"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_5_37323-37390",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "37323-37390",
      "markText": "“过来点，”他又说，“我读到你的字条时，就像五脏六腑一下子全给掏空了。真是这样的。如果你真的走了，我就会觉得身体里什么都没有留下了。”",
      "totalCount": 1008,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=37323&rangeEnd=37390",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=37323&rangeEnd=37390"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_5_27938-27978",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "27938-27978",
      "markText": "我一直感到需要过一种更为真实的生活。我知道在这一点上我永远也无法得到你们的理解。",
      "totalCount": 924,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=27938&rangeEnd=27978",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=27938&rangeEnd=27978"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_5_27608-27654",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "27608-27654",
      "markText": "她把他看作是二人未来生活的设计师，她自己则甘于当俘虏，她的顺从既是理所当然的也是心悦诚服的。",
      "totalCount": 840,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=27608&rangeEnd=27654",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=27608&rangeEnd=27654"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_8_29390-29430",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "29390-29430",
      "markText": "她像更谙世故的人在等待非分之想、自然康复或是此等好事时那样，仅仅是怀着希望而已。",
      "totalCount": 792,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=29390&rangeEnd=29430",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=29390&rangeEnd=29430"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_4_1140-1210",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1140-1210",
      "markText": "但如果故事背景设在现代世界，人物关心的事物对你而言很熟悉，你如此深陷于它，以至于夜不释卷，那就存在一种风险：这样的阅读会不会仅仅是一种消遣？",
      "totalCount": 735,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1140&rangeEnd=1210",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1140&rangeEnd=1210"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_5_18488-18574",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "18488-18574",
      "markText": "他什么时候都冲着她发火。就像是心里有多恨她似的。她不管做什么都是做得不对的，不管说什么都是说错的。跟他一起过真要把她逼疯了。有时候她觉得自己已经疯了。有时候又觉得是他疯了。",
      "totalCount": 731,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=18488&rangeEnd=18574",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=18488&rangeEnd=18574"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_12_15411-15481",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "15411-15481",
      "markText": "“我们不写信，写信不是一个好主意。我们只要互相记得，明年夏天我们将重新见面。你不用通知我，来就是了。如果你的感觉还没有变的话，你来就是了。”",
      "totalCount": 697,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=15411&rangeEnd=15481",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=15411&rangeEnd=15481"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_5_28445-28504",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "28445-28504",
      "markText": "她真是想象不出来。她会怎样去搭乘地铁或是电车，去照料陌生的马匹，去跟不熟识的人说话，每天都生活在不是克拉克的人群之中。",
      "totalCount": 676,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=28445&rangeEnd=28504",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=28445&rangeEnd=28504"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_5_13805-13861",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "13805-13861",
      "markText": "不过，在西尔维亚眼里，这就是一朵艳丽的花朵，它的花瓣在她的内心乱哄哄热辣辣地张开着，就像是更年期的一次重新来潮。",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13805&rangeEnd=13861",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=13805&rangeEnd=13861"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_5_10421-10471",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "10421-10471",
      "markText": "“你受到了伤害。你受到骚扰和侮辱，也就是我受到了伤害和侮辱，因为你是我老婆。这是个有关尊严的问题。”",
      "totalCount": 624,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=30599279&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10421&rangeEnd=10471",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3cf3255071d2e86f3cf3371?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10421&rangeEnd=10471"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "30599279_6_3287-3404",
